sense.gloss: to come to a dead end, to come to a standstill, to reach a deadlock, to reach an impasse, to reach a stalemate

sdata.j: ↑愚者↑↓ぐしゃ↓はすぐ↑奥↑↓おく↓の↑手↑↓て↓を↑出↑↓だ↓し↑行↑↓|い↓き↑詰↑↓づ↓まる|。
sdata.e: A fool's bolt is soon shot.

sdata.j: それは↑息↑↓|いき↓づまる|ような↑試合↑↓しあい↓だった。
sdata.e: It was a breath-taking close game.
